author: jholmes
msg: Log a warning if user specifies a namespace and action with the <s:form> tag and the action is not found in the namespace. Right now this fails silently and the user gets an HTTP 404 typically. I've had this happen to me and it took a little while to realize I had the wrong namespace or action name. This warning should help users figure out the issue faster by giving them a heads up.
